"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-lifestyle-celeb-news-local-celebs-zenani-kraai-from-langas-blue-turf-to-the-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.6520973189433281, \"rank\": 0.5334949788377186, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbLifestyle\\u00bbCeleb News\\u00bbLocal Celebs\\u00bbZenani Kraai: From Langa's blue turf to the Paris Olympics  Zenani Kraai, a highly skilled hockey player from the township of Langa, is proudly making his Olympic debut for South Africa.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.6520973189433281, \"rank\": 0.5334949788377186, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}, {\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zenani\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\"}, {\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}, {\"begin\": 385, \"end\": 397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 1.6604483466161783e-12, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zenani Kraai, a talented hockey player from Langa, is set to make his Olympic debut in Paris.\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 400, \"end\": 406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zenani\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\"}, {\"begin\": 444, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}, {\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999982619556, \"rank\": 1.7379003213305944e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This milestone marks a significant achievement for Kraai, who has overcome numerous challenges to reach this point.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kraai received the life-changing news while at home with his family.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 679, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A dream come true,\\\" he recalled.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember feeling happy, and my family was just really happy and congratulated me.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They told me to just play my game and that it was my hard work that got me here.\\\"\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kraai has played a crucial role in the South African Men's Hockey team, according toGood Things Guy.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team secured their Olympic qualification by defeating Egypt 2-1 in the final last November.\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1044, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9931742170664092, \"rank\": 0.006865052425364581, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More recently, they beat Pakistan 4-3 in the bronze medal playoff at the FIH Nations Cup in Poland.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999912498752493, \"rank\": 8.749032130234627e-06, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These victories have been vital in preparing the team for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With 18 Caps for the men's team, Kraai reminisced about his first Cap at the Azlan Shah Cup in Malaysia in November 2022, according to theInternational Hockey Federation.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 0.988537574197153, \"rank\": 0.01159505781546991, \"text\": \"Malaysia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember crying the first time I sang the national anthem,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This highlighted his deep pride and emotional connection to his country.\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kraai's introduction to hockey came through community outreach projects.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Initially a football player like many children in Langa, a friend's invitation to a hockey clinic changed his path.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1699, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I eventually found myself skipping football sessions to play hockey,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And eventually, hockey was the only sport I was playing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Currently playing for Langa Hockey Club, Kraai has represented both his province and country at various levels.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1934, \"end\": 1939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zenani Kraai emphasised the importance of accessible community sports programmes.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2025, \"end\": 2031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zenani\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zenani_Mandela-Dlamini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is especially important in areas like Langa where they are more available compared to other townships.\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2151, \"end\": 2156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These programmes showed me that success was possible in my situation,\\\" he noted.\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kraai's journey has not been easy.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up in Langa, he faced social and economic challenges.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"score\": 0.9999998751368444, \"rank\": 1.2486310913718193e-07, \"text\": \"Langa\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langhe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He missed birthdays, milestones, and family occasions to train and attend national team camps.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During difficult times, he leaned on his family and coach for support.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Am I ever going to make it where I see myself?\\\"\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"he often wondered.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But their encouragement kept him going.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His self-resilience also played a key role.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Things will not stay like this, someday it will change,\\\" he would remind himself.\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He believed that hard work would eventually pay off.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do not cheat yourself.\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Put in the hours and the selections and results will reflect your hard work.\\\"\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Kraai, success is not just about personal achievements.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I can inspire others through the way I have walked, or to walk a better path\\u2026 not the achievements but to be an example to those who look like and have lived a life like mine, then I have found success,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking ahead to the Olympics, Kraai aims to contribute to his team's success, according toSA Hockey.\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The team culture brings people from different walks of life together,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we all have the same goal and stick together, we will be able to tackle anything that comes our way.\\\"\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked for advice to aspiring Olympians, Kraai shared, \\\"Keep showing up, despite it raining, you are not feeling good, whatever's going on.\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3679, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because when you show up and put the time in, all the excuses flush away.\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So get there, play hockey, enjoy and express yourself.\\\"\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kraai's journey is a testament to his dedication and resilience.\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As hepreparesfor the Olympics, his story continues to inspire.\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 3940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The South African Men's Hockey team is in the final stages of fundraising for their Olympic campaign.\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 4043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To support them, visitFund Your Passion.\", \"from\": 4044, \"to\": 4084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Community sports programmes are essential for youth development as they provide a structured and supportive environment for children to engage in physical activity.\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These programmes help foster teamwork, discipline, and social skills, while also promoting a healthy lifestyle.\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What do you think?\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or by emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.comor sending a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4497, \"end\": 4505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9992188063190691, \"rank\": 0.0007818044216767392, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also follow@TheSAnews on XandThe South African on Facebookfor the latest news.\", \"from\": 4525, \"to\": 4611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4613, \"end\": 4616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Jets\", \"score\": 0.7617522425410005, \"rank\": 0.3127627909733376, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q4498974\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Jets\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Jets\"}, {\"begin\": 4617, \"end\": 4619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9155218135016442, \"rank\": 0.09027439098219257, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 5078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4841, \"end\": 4849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9992188063190691, \"rank\": 0.0007818044216767392, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orlando Pirates are reportedly set to welcome a new staff member in former Stellenbosch FC Head of Recruitment Brendon Fourie.\", \"from\": 5080, \"to\": 5206, \"entities\": [{